  "text": "To study the localization of OsDr1 and OsDrAp1 in plant cells, we inserted the coding regions of OsDr1 and OsDrAp1 into the vector pRTL2-mGFP [CITATION_1] to generate pOsDr1/mGFP and pOsDrAp1/mGFP constructs (Figure 3A) , which contain OsDr1/mGFP and OsDrAp1/mGFP (D) Interaction of recombinant OsDr1 and OsDrAp1 in vitro. Lane 1, the gel was stained with Coomassie blue; lanes 2 and 3, the proteins were blotted onto nitrocellulose membranes and incubated with His tag antibody (lane 2) and T7 tag antibody (lane 3); lane 4, the proteins blotted onto nitrocellulose membrane were denatured, renatured, and incubated with purified OsDr1 and with the T7 tag antibody.",
