      "span_text": "To study the localization of OsDr1 and OsDrAp1 in plant cells, we inserted the coding regions of OsDr1 and OsDrAp1 into the vector pRTL2-mGFP to generate pOsDr1/mGFP and pOsDrAp1/mGFP constructs (Figure 3A), which contain OsDr1/mGFP and OsDrAp1/mGFP (D) Interaction of recombinant OsDr1 and OsDrAp1 in vitro."
